奶奶，当他们践踏日裔美国人，

307
00:18:26.043 --> 00:18:30.096
our Japanese-American neighbors off to internment camps?
将他们关押起来时，您在哪儿？

308
00:18:30.096 --> 00:18:32.485
And Grandpa, where were you  when they were beating
爷爷，当那些非洲裔美国人

