但我认为现在已经有了 去改变这一现状的机会了。

347
00:21:00.161 --> 00:21:05.238
CA: But to make this happen, you have to look at each part in the chain --
CA: 要让这成为现实， 你需要关注整条链上的每一个环节——

348
00:21:05.241 --> 00:21:07.496
the police, who else?
警方，还有呢？

349
00:21:07.496 --> 00:21:09.777
GH: So that's the thing  about law enforcement,
GH: 关于法律的实施，

350
00:21:09.777 --> 00:21:11.220
it starts out with the police,
从警方开始，

351
00:21:11.220 --> 00:21:13.903
they're the front end of the pipeline of justice,
他们维护正义，奋斗在前线，

352
00:21:13.903 --> 00:21:15.850
but they hand if off to the prosecutors,
他们将罪犯送到检察官手里，

